from other lands to share in the ministry.

01:01:36.609 --> 01:01:40.913 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The response to the good news
is very encouraging.

01:01:40.913 --> 01:01:44.650 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
More than 870,000 Bible studies

01:01:44.650 --> 01:01:46.819 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are conducted every month.

01:01:46.819 --> 01:01:51.290 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
On average, about 40 people
are baptized every day,

01:01:51.290 --> 01:01:53.326 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and seven new congregations

01:01:53.326 --> 01:01:55.328 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are formed every month.

01:01:56.696 --> 01:01:59.632 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is the Obudu Ranch Congregation.

01:01:59.632 --> 01:02:04.303 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Their territory is beautiful,
vast, and mountainous

01:02:04.303 --> 01:02:06.372 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—literally in the clouds.

01:02:06.372 --> 01:02:08.374 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Twenty-three publishers,

01:02:08.374 --> 01:02:12.879 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
including two special pioneers, serve here.

01:02:12.879 --> 01:02:16.516 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To reach areas only accessible by foot,

01:02:16.516 --> 01:02:19.852 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the publishers
sometimes walk for eight hours.

01:02:19.852 --> 01:02:23.489 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The terrain is challenging,
but the long walk 

01:02:23.489 --> 01:02:26.559 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
provides opportunities
for upbuilding association.

01:02:27.827 --> 01:02:29.929 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
After working the territory, our brothers

01:02:29.929 --> 01:02:32.565 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
stay overnight and walk back

01:02:32.565 --> 01:02:34.801 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
another eight hours.

01:02:36.502 --> 01:02:39.071 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our brothers and sisters
in the Obudu Ranch Congregation

01:02:39.071 --> 01:02:42.108 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
send their warm love and greetings!

01:02:43.976 --> 01:02:46.446 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
From the World Headquarters
of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

01:02:46.446 --> 01:02:49.882 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this is JW Broadcasting.

